  <brief_title>Phase 2A Open Label Safety Study of Fovista® (Anti-PDGF BB) Regimen Administered in Combination With Anti-VEGF Therapy to Study Sub-Retinal Fibrosis in Neovascular AMD</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
