    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Subjects will be administered Fovista® (anti-PDGF BB) plus anti-VEGF as a &quot;Pre-Treatment&quot; or as a &quot;Simultaneous&quot; regimen followed by quarterly administration.</description>
  </arm_group>
